OL,4,CPolice need clearer guidance on Tasers
OL,5,C- watchdog
OL,6, Police forces must be given clearer
OL,7, guidance about when they can use Tasers
OL,8, to control suspects, according to the
OL,9, police watchdog.
OL,11,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,12,FConduct (IOPC) has reviewed
OL,13,Fcontroversial cases of Taser use.
OL,15,FIt found black people were more likely
OL,16,Fto face a Taser and some officers were
OL,17,Fnot considering the risk of injury to
OL,18,Fvulnerable people.
OL,20,FBut police chiefs say the IOPC report
OL,21,Fis vague and lacking in detail.
